caption:
This weekend RnR hosted another South Florida Retreat, joining forces with @flourishlawgroup for a niche audience: Women in Law! This was a unique experience for our attendees with the goal to showcase how incorporating daily wellness can be one of the most empowering tools available to high performing professionals. Here’s what our retreat included:

🔆 outdoor yoga & sound bath
🔆 expert panel on wellness & stress management 
🔆 journal & group conversations 
🔆 networking, new connections and more!

Thank you to our incredible sponsors and panelist:
@trippscott50 @thedailydripofficial #ISA @haliczerpettisschwammattorneys @collectively_us @dr.shivanigupta @kaylaaamorann @lawyer.britt @simplyclaims @lawyerlaurenklein
